keyValuePair.Value: Can your boys still make Europe?
Your target was always to bring European football to the club. Recent results have made that look less likely. Can your team break out of this current slump?
Everything's still possible.
It won't be easy now to qualify for Europe. But we're still in the middle of the scrap for places. We have to work our hardest to make sure we take our chance.
I want us to fight for it now.
All we can control now is our own performances. We can't worry about anyone else. If we can be at our best, we'll see where the rest of the season takes us.
The lads have to be positive.
The lads have to be positive.
We've been on a poor run but I'm more bothered by the fact that the players have been looking sorry for themselves. They have to be positive. Our destiny's in our own hands.

Can you still make it a top-half finish?
Your team should definitely be competing towards the top of the table. Recent results have seen you slip away a bit, though. Can your players find their form again this season?
We're up for the challenge.
We know we've made it difficult to reach our targets for the season now. But this is a good squad of players and we know that, with some hard work, we're still capable of a strong finish.
That's the challenge for the lads.
We're working hard in training to put things right. Hopefully that'll be reflected in better results sooner rather than later. There's still a lot to fight for this season.
Let's not have any regrets.
Let's not have any regrets.

Are you struggling to reach the playoffs now?
Just recently your team's struggled to find any consistency. The playoffs look a big ask now. Do you still think your boys can re-discover a bit of form and make it?
It's not going to be easy.
We've given ourselves a lot to do to reach the playoffs now, for sure. But this is a talented team. If we work hard and get our rhythm back, anything's still possible.
We won't stop fighting.
Nothing's ever clear-cut in this division and we know we've given ourselves a lot to do if we're to make the playoffs. But while there's still a chance, we won't stop fighting for it.
The lads have to find some pride.

Can you still win promotion?
Your team's just struggled a bit of late and that means your promotion ambitions are under real threat. Can your boys get their challenge back on track?
We have to stop the slide.
Look, it's not going to be easy now. This is a super-competitive division. But we have to focus on our own performances. We're still good enough to go up.
Let's focus on our own form.

The players have to pull together.

This is a real challenge.

We'll keep fighting, for sure.

Can your boys still qualify for Europe.
You were looking on course for a UEFA Europa League position but this run of poor results has left you with ground to make up. Can the boys recover?
We know it won't be easy now.
We've definitely given ourselves a lot to do but we all know where we want to be at the end of the season. It's going to take a lot of hard work. But I believe the boys are ready for that.
We're relying on others.
We've put ourselves in a position where maybe qualification isn't just in our hands. All we can do now is give it everything and hope that the season plays out in our favour.

Can your boys still make it?
Your team's stuttered at a really important stage of the season. Suddenly, your target of qualifying for the UEFA Champions League looks in doubt. Can your boys recover now?
This won't be easy now.
We know we've put ourselves in a more difficult position with some poor results. But the boys know that, if we work hard enough, we're still in with a chance.
We owe it to ourselves.
You can't switch form on and off like a tap. But we know what we've got to do to qualify. We'll give everything now to fulfil our ambitions.

Are you out of the title race?
Your team's struggled to find consistency recently and your title bid has faltered. Can the players get their challenge back on track and give you a great end to the season?
We've got to make up ground.
We've definitely made this hard for ourselves. We have to focus. We know what we want to achieve and we have to win games now to give us any chance of getting there.
We need to find some form.
